<div class="bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row pt-2 pb-2 border-bottom">
      <div class="col-sm-12 ">
        <div class="sticky-top sticky-bar">
          <a href="<%= root_path %>">
            <%= image_tag "best-vet-logo.png", alt: "Best Vet Logo", class: "mx-auto d-block", width: "200px" %>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-success p-3">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h1 class="text-white">Your Trusted Online Veterinary Clinic</h1>
          <p class="text-white small mt-1">
            Welcome to our Online Veterinary Clinic, where quality care meets convenience and speed.
            Our dedicated team of experienced veterinarians is here to provide expert guidance and support for your beloved pets, all from the comfort of your own home.
            Schedule a call now
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-3  col-sm-12 bg-white text-center col-md-6 round">
          <h5><strong>Need assistance?</strong></h5>
          <%= link_to "I need an emergency call", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-round btn-success btn-blocked mt-3' %>
          <%= link_to "Schedule a call", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-outline-success btn-blocked mt-3' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="p-4 col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
        <h2 class="display-5">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase-medical text-success"></i>
          <strong class="ms-2">Trusted vets</strong>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted small">
          Our online clinic is home to a team of trusted veterinarians who are committed to delivering compassionate care for your beloved pets.
          With years of experience and a deep understanding of animal health, our vets prioritize the well-being of your furry companions above all else.
          Whether it's a routine check-up, preventive care, or urgent treatment, you can trust our dedicated team to provide the highest level of care and support for your pet's health journey.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Get help", new_user_registration_path, class: 'text-success small text-decoration-none' %>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
        <h2 class="display-5">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-message text-success"></i>
          <strong class="ms-2">Forum</strong>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted small">
          Our veterinary forum is a community-driven platform where pet owners can seek expert advice and guidance from our team of experienced veterinarians.
          If you have any questions about nutrition, behavior, or medical concerns, our vets are here to provide personalized answers tailored to your pet's specific needs.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Ask a question", categories_path, class: 'text-success small text-decoration-none' %>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
        <h2 class="display-5">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-dog text-success"></i>
          <strong class="ms-2">Save records</strong>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted small">
          Managing your pet's health records can be overwhelming, but our clinic offers a solution.
          With our centralized pet health record system, you can conveniently store all of your pet's important medical information in one secure location.
          From vaccination records to medication history and vet visit summaries, everything you need to keep your pet healthy is easily accessible whenever you need it.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Start now", new_user_registration_path, class: 'text-success small text-decoration-none' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
